title: ASK ANDY:  Product Development and a Primer on Core Values
description: (1) Why are core values important and (2) How do you make a good product great? In this ASK ANDY episode of The MFCEO Project, Andy Frisella answers questions from listeners.  Vaughn Kohler joins him for the conversation.
